nodes.text: Part of the Alliance to Restore the Republic, this group was composed primarily of BTL Y-wing starfighters and a Recusant-class light destroyer. In 0 BBY, this group attacked the Imperial controlled planet Ord Biniir in what would later be known as the First Battle of Ord Biniir. The group managed to capture the planet for the Alliance and defeat the 233rd Imperial Fighter Group.
